# Regenerable artifacts from record.ts / compose.ts / Remotion render
recordings/
screenshots/
output/
timing-data.json
test-report.md
error-log.json

# Remotion staging (B-roll copied from docs/demo/broll/ at render time)
video/public/shot*.mp4
video/public/recordings/
